COPYRIGHT 2004 BLUE CROSS/BLUE SHIELD OF KANSAS CITY 


JOB NAME:     IdsClmRemitHistFkey

DESCRIPTION:     Takes the sorted file and applies the primary key.   Preps the file for the foreign key lookup process that follows.
      

INPUTS: Primary Key output file.
	
  
HASH FILES:     hf_recycle  


TRANSFORMS:  
                           

PROCESSING:
Product key lookup - 
                GetFkeyProd( TRIM(  ClsPlnCrfIn.SRC_SYS_CD ),   ClsPlnCrfIn.CLS_PLN_SK,  TRIM (ClsPlnCrfIn.PROD_ID ),   "Y")


OUTPUTS: Load File for remit history table.

MODIFICATIONS:
            Steph Goddard   04/2004  -   Originally Programmed
            Brent Leland       09/10/2004  -  Added default rows for UNK and NA
                                                           -  Added link partitioner
            Steph Goddard   09/13/2005    Added calculated payment amount indicator
            Steph Goddard   02/16/2006   sequencer changes
            Brent Leland       08/07/2006    Added current run cycle to output records.  Without the current run cycle, error recycle records would have an old run cycle and would be removed in delete process.
            Ralph Tucker    10/03/2006 Removed the following fields: CLM_REMIT_HIST-pAYMTOVRD_CD_SK
                                                                                                          CHK_PD_DT_SK
                                                                                                          CHK_NET_PAYMT_AMT
                                                                                                          CHK_NO
                                                                                                          CHK_SEQ_NO
                                                                                                          CHK_PAYE_NM
                                                                                                          CHK_PAYMT_REF_ID
                                                                                                          CLM_REMIT_HIST_PAYMTMETH_CD_SK
                                                             Added field:  PCA_PD_AMT          


MODIFICATIONS:
Developer                Date                 Project/Altiris #      Change Description                                                                                                Development Project      Code Reviewer          Date Reviewed       
------------------              --------------------     ------------------------      -----------------------------------------------------------------------                                                         --------------------------------       -------------------------------   ----------------------------       
Bhoomi Dasari         2008-08-12      3567(Primary Key)    Added new parameter SrcSysCdSk and passing it directly from source                  devlIDS                          Steph Goddard         08/18/2008
SAndrew                 2009-06-23      #3833 Remit Alt Chrg      Added two new fields to end of file and to shared container                             devlIDSnew                   Steph Goddard           07/01/2009
                                                                                               ALT_CHRG_IN and ALT_CHRG_PROV_WRTOFF_AMT
                                                                                      













































































